The paper discusses the challenges of building and deploying software on high-end computing systems, which is a topic related to distributed computing (cs.DC) and software engineering (cs.SE). The focus on containers as a solution suggests a connection to programming languages (cs.PL) and architecture (cs.AR). Finally, the mention of GPU accelerators and specialized networking indicates a potential connection to distributed systems (cs.Distributed).
